---
title: Mediterranean Roasted Eggplant Fusilli with Greek Salad Cheese & Toasted Almonds
description: Add layers of flavour to fusilli with an array of rainbow veggies roasted in Mediterranean-inspired seasonings. Paired with a rich tomato sauce and aromatic basil leaves, your finished dish will be transformed into a taste sensation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-nz-mediterranean-fusilli-roasted-eggplant-600f0167.jpg
